collection.name: Angry Ape Army Evolution Collection
collection.description:
The Angry Ape Army have modified their own kind to create "Evolved Apes." 
These lab grown apes are now roaming the metaverse destroying and taking control of all that come in it's path. Take control of an "Evolved Ape" and have superior battle advantage or spawn a Goliath x Golem by combining 4 evo apes. 


**Join the Revolution!!!**
